# Fuzzing — root-level (legacy) and per-crate cargo-fuzz layouts.
# Per-parser harnesses live at crates/*/fuzz/ (ADR-0018 §§3–4); the
# corpus is **never** committed — the nightly workflow uploads it as an
# artifact. See docs/runbooks/fuzzing.md.
/fuzz/artifacts/
/fuzz/corpus/
/fuzz/coverage/
/fuzz/target/
crates/*/fuzz/target/
crates/*/fuzz/corpus/
crates/*/fuzz/artifacts/
crates/*/fuzz/coverage/
crates/*/fuzz/Cargo.lock

